&quot;Guns And Horses&quot; was the third single from <a href="http://www.last.fm/music/Ellie+Goulding" class="bbcode_artist">Ellie Goulding</a>'s debut album <a title="Ellie Goulding - Lights" href="http://www.last.fm/music/Ellie+Goulding/Lights" class="bbcode_album">Lights</a>. It was released on 17th May 2010. The song is the first track on <a title="Ellie Goulding - Lights" href="http://www.last.fm/music/Ellie+Goulding/Lights" class="bbcode_album">Lights</a>.

 Goulding told Sky Songs about this tune. &quot;I wrote Guns And Horses about a romance that began online. I wanted the guy to feel more than he did for me but through no fault of his own he couldn't. It's a song about frustration essentially. My producer made me laugh at the end, I can't repeat what he called me though.&quot;

